{"tid":1654292,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"試著說加強和理非，不要說勇武休息","createTime":"2019-10-14T14:01:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T02:00:30.000Z","uid":37396,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"03541e96f9857fd88736e2cf839e6658eb9c0c70","tid":1654292,"uid":37396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:01:09.000Z","msg":"選舉近了<br />\n叫勇武停嘅聲音可以預料有增無減<br />\n希望各位記住我地走到黎今時今日係因為<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">和勇合一，缺一不可</span><br />\n<br />\n如果驚勇武傷害國際形象，令人權法過唔倒（其實我好質疑，因為美國過唔過係睇對美國嘅利益，而唔係啲人和平定勇武，話係因為勇武只不過係藉口）<br />\n我地做嘅唔係停止勇武<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而係加強和理非</span><br />\n<br />\n無論係區議會選舉定係人權法<br />\n對我地嚟講都只係助攻<br />\n到頭來都係要靠我地自己比壓力政府<br />\n再加上政府其實想取消區議會就可以取消（緊急法都已經出埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n根本佢唔會理你和平定勇武，唔通你覺得政府會眼白白睇住建制派仆晒街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嚟緊我地必須要有更多好似今日咁嘅和理非式集會<br />\n但同時勇武絕對唔可以停<br />\n我相信我地一定會贏！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 <br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"17abd4f6661cf814f5bc3f7b0a81da28ceddb316","tid":1654292,"uid":37396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:02:48.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"3cd2b9ed843757d44bde77ca81b758abdecce447","tid":1654292,"uid":37396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T14:31:20.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"d5adc774df8d9aa45227f9a6ca937d8b3b456d97","tid":1654292,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:21:02.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n方向正確"},{"pid":"e05ee8005828120267ce67d5bb56ae7d0c4678e3","tid":1654292,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:52:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab565f5e484060e85cc69af1a8815d67833ef66d","tid":1654292,"uid":37396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T17:25:31.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"1390314f8f7879bf64370084bac5863b04034560","tid":1654292,"uid":30601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T17:38:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ba09538698082c6f6eff635d69b806d03b03b2","tid":1654292,"uid":89873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T17:40:30.000Z","msg":"借個位黎用吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我要真．文宣!!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1654696\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1654696</a>"},{"pid":"c2d6d168ecb261a765542c27052235c16f27623f","tid":1654292,"uid":66074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T17:41:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf0876f2a72bb423b3b667d91379d663888f7b88","tid":1654292,"uid":66074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T17:42:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c8e66883d81553920a12d3d40f4ed2e0a1b9650","tid":1654292,"uid":37396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T02:00:30.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}